queries.sql:
select *
        from tbl_users as tu, tbl_position as tp
        where tu.position = tp.posID
        and tu.firm = 1
        and tu.userID != 1

select wpID,wp.added_by,wp.client, wp.auditor, wp.supervisor,wp.audmanager, wp.firm,wp.jobdur,wp.financial_year,wp.end_financial_year,wp.status,wp.remarks,wp.added_on, (select COUNT(*) from tbl_client_files_c1 as tc1 where tc1.workpaper = wp.wpID and tc1.clientID = wp.client) as x1, (select COUNT(*) from tbl_client_files_c2 as tc2 where tc2.workpaper = wp.wpID and tc2.clientID = wp.client) as x2, (select COUNT(*) from tbl_client_files_c3 as tc3 where tc3.workpaper = wp.wpID and tc3.clientID = wp.client) as x3, (select COUNT(*) from tbl_client_files_c1 as tc1 where tc1.workpaper = wp.wpID and tc1.clientID = wp.client and updated_on IS NOT NULL) as y1, (select COUNT(*) from tbl_client_files_c2 as tc2 where tc2.workpaper = wp.wpID and tc2.clientID = wp.client and updated_on IS NOT NULL) as y2, (select COUNT(*) from tbl_client_files_c3 as tc3 where tc3.workpaper = wp.wpID and tc3.clientID = wp.client and updated_on IS NOT NULL) as y3, tc.name as cli, tc.org from tbl_workpaper as wp, tbl_clients as tc where wp.firm = 1 and tc.cID = wp.client and wp.financial_year = '2024'
